# HUD::IS_ONLINE_POLICIES_MENU_ACTIVE

## Summary
Returns if the online policies menu is open

## Returns
* **BOOL**

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Returns the same as IS_SOCIAL_CLUB_ACTIVE
